videos.headline: Arkansas' Pittman ecstatic about bowl eligibility
videos.description: After becoming bowl eligible for the first time since 2016 with a win over MS State, head coach Sam Pittman shares his excitement.

videos.headline: Johnson's last-second TD seals wild victory for Hogs
videos.description: In a back-and-forth thriller, Arkansas' Dominique Johnson runs in the game-winning touchdown as the Razorbacks upset No. 17 Mississippi State, 31-28.

videos.headline: Leach announces open tryouts at kicker after Miss. State's loss
